United Technologies Corp said itsboard authorized management at its discretion to buy up to sixmln shares of the company's common stock in the open market.    "We are taking this action because the price of the stockrepresents an excellent buying opportunity," the company saidin a statement.    The military, commercial and industrial products companyhad about 131.6 mln shares outstanding at Sept 30.    Its shares were trading off 1-3/4 at 37-1/4 late in theday. Reuter&#3;